ðŸŒŸ Main Features and Descriptions

1. User Management

This feature allows users to register, log in, and manage their profiles. It ensures secure access to the platform and personalizes the user experience.

2. Property Management

Hosts can list, update, or remove their properties. This feature is essential for maintaining an up-to-date property catalog that guests can browse and book from.

3. Booking System

Users can view available properties and book them for specific dates. It handles availability, confirms reservations, and ensures a smooth booking process.

4. Review System

Guests can leave reviews and ratings after their stay. This helps build trust among users and encourages property owners to maintain quality standards.

5. Payment Integration

Secure payment processing is handled through this feature. It supports transactions, tracks payments, and ensures financial records are accurately tied to bookings.
